Omnistudio Data Mapper Extract Action for Integration Procedures
 The Data Mapper Extract Action calls the specified Data Mapper Extract to read data from Salesforce and returns it to the Integration Procedure.
 For Integration Procedure examples that include at least one Data Mapper Extract Action, see Process Arrays Using Loop Blocks and Handle Errors Using Try-Catch Blocks.

Omnistudio Data Mapper Extract Action Properties for Integration Procedures
 These properties are unique to or function in a unique manner in Data Mapper Extract Actions. The Data Mapper Extract Action calls the specified Data Mapper Extract to read data from Salesforce and returns it to the Integration Procedure.
